name: Squiggly Clock
description:
This piece is a fully customizable interactive clock. Coded from scratch using p5.js. 

Tap/Click to switch between monochrome and color mode.

Key Map: 
+,- : To speed up/down the arcs 
c   : To toggle fill/line mode
x,z : To change the colors of arc and frame
g,h : To adjust thickness of the arc
q,w : To adjust arm length
k,l : To adjust arc spacing
s:  : To save your settings to the browser storage / Settings are cleared, when browser cache is cleared
